    <item>
      <title>Maintenance Log - Twelfth Week: User Profiles, Employee Admin Actions, and Form Patterns</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-twelfthweek/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>cph-ja472@stud.ek.dk (Jesper Andersen)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-twelfthweek/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Devlog Week 12: User Profiles, Employee Admin Actions, and Form Patterns&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;devlog-week-12-user-profiles-employee-admin-actions-and-form-patterns&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#devlog-week-12-user-profiles-employee-admin-actions-and-form-patterns&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This entry covers the employee-facing parts of the UI: profile views, edit flows, admin actions, and the form patterns used to keep components maintainable.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What Changed&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;what-changed&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#what-changed&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;UserProfile&lt;/code&gt; supports both &amp;ldquo;me&amp;rdquo; and viewing other employees via dynamic route params&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Profile page extracted into focused subcomponents:&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;EditProfileForm&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;AdminActions&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;PasswordChangeForm&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Form handling uses a mix of controlled inputs and a &lt;code&gt;FormData&lt;/code&gt; approach (when appropriate)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;useEffect&lt;/code&gt; race-condition prevention via an &lt;code&gt;ignore&lt;/code&gt; flag to avoid setting state after unmount&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Admin-only employee actions (deactivate/reactivate) gated by role and disallowed on own profile&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;User Profile: “Me” vs “Other Employee”&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;user-profile-me-vs-other-employee&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#user-profile-me-vs-other-employee&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The profile route supports multiple entry points:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
